# Purpose: Ignore local caches, secrets, build output, and runtime state for the multi-agent system.
# Input/Output: Git excludes generated files from commits and PRs.
# Invariants: Secrets and runtime databases never belong in version control.
# Debugging: If a file is missing from Git unexpectedly, inspect this file first.

.env
.env.local
.venv/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
data/
logs/
reports/
workspace/
tmp/
node_modules/
